<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Noor Fragrances</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/user/aboutUs.css">
    
</head>
<body>
    <header>
          <%- include("../../views/partials/user/header") %>
    </header>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero-section" id="hero">
        <div class="hero-background"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="hero-text">
                <h1 class="hero-title">Our Story of Excellence</h1>
                <p class="hero-description">Founded in 2025, Noor Fragrances has quickly become a trusted name for fragrance connoisseurs alike. By collaborating with world-renowned perfumers and sourcing the finest ingredients, we offer an exquisite range of signature scents that cater to every personality and occasion.</p>
                <p class="hero-description">With over 10,000+ sales every month, we are dedicated to delivering premium quality, exceptional service, and a luxurious shopping experience. Join us in redefining elegance, one fragrance at a time!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image">
                <img src="/img/logo/ChatGPT Image May 14, 2025, 11_17_54 PM.png" alt="Noor Fragrances Brand Image">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-down" onclick="document.getElementById('stats').scrollIntoView({behavior: 'smooth'})">
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Stats Section -->
    <section class="stats-section" id="stats">
        <div class="stats-container">
            <div class="stats-header">
                <h2>Our Impact</h2>
                <p>Since our inception, we've grown rapidly to become a leader in the luxury fragrance market, with an expanding community of customers and partners.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="stats-grid">
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-number">10.5k</div>
                    <div class="stat-text">Sellers active on our site</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="stat-box highlighted">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-award"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-number">33k</div>
                    <div class="stat-text">Monthly Products Sold</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-shopping-bag"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-number">45.5k</div>
                    <div class="stat-text">Customers active on our site</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <div class="stat-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-dollar-sign"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-number">25k</div>
                    <div class="stat-text">Annual gross sales in our site</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Team Section -->
    <section class="team-section" id="team">
        <div class="team-container">
            <div class="team-header">
                <h2>Leadership</h2>
                <p>Meet the visionaries behind Noor Fragrances, whose passion for perfumery and business acumen has guided our journey.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-grid">
                <div class="founder-card">
                    <img class="founder-image" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dlf7ygi2x/image/upload/v1747292146/portfolio-img3_pn7x9c.jpg" alt="image">
                    <div class="founder-info">
                        <h3>Muhammed Shibili.k</h3>
                        <div class="founder-position">Founder & Chairman</div>
                        <p class="founder-bio">With over a decade of experience in the luxury fragrance industry, our founder has revolutionized how we experience scents. Their vision of creating personalized, high-quality fragrances accessible to everyone drives our company's mission.</p>
                        <div class="social-links">
                            <a href="#">
                                <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#">
                                <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#">
                                <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="founder-card">
                    <img class="founder-image" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dlf7ygi2x/image/upload/v1747290411/3b62fb4a-0210-425a-8702-29ac70967026_bu6dec.jpg" alt="image">
                    <div class="founder-info">
                        <h3>Akhila Tarol</h3>
                        <div class="founder-position">Chief Creative Officer</div>
                        <p class="founder-bio">As our CCO, Akhila brings her exceptional sense of smell and creative vision to our scent development process. With a background in fine arts and perfumery, she ensures each fragrance tells a unique story.</p>
                        <div class="social-links">
                            <a href="#">
                                <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#">
                                <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#">
                                <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="founder-card">
                    <img class="founder-image" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dlf7ygi2x/image/upload/v1747289303/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_10.01.51_AM_mynqvl.jpg" alt="image">
                    <div class="founder-info">
                        <h3>Sahad Saleel</h3>
                        <div class="founder-position">Operations Director</div>
                        <p class="founder-bio">Sahad oversees our global supply chain and operations. His expertise in logistics ensures that we maintain the highest quality standards while delivering products efficiently to customers worldwide.</p>
                        <div class="social-links">
                            <a href="#">
                                <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#">
                                <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#">
                                <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="founder-card">
                    <img class="founder-image" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dlf7ygi2x/image/upload/v1747289304/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_10.03.17_AM_ynfw7i.jpg" alt="image">
                    <div class="founder-info">
                        <h3>Abdul Hakeem</h3>
                        <div class="founder-position">Marketing Director</div>
                        <p class="founder-bio">Leading our marketing initiatives, Hakeem has built Noor Fragrances into a recognized luxury brand. His innovative digital strategies and deep understanding of consumer behavior have been key to our rapid growth.</p>
                        <div class="social-links">
                            <a href="#">
                                <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#">
                                <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
                            </a>
                            <a href="#">
                                <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer >
         <%- include("../../views/partials/user/footer") %>
    </footer>
    
    <script>
        // Scroll effect for navigation
        window.addEventListener('scroll', function() {
            const nav = document.querySelector('.nav-container');
            if (window.scrollY > 50) {
                nav.classList.add('nav-scrolled');
            } else {
                nav.classList.remove('nav-scrolled');
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>